{"type": "article", "id": 20684, "title": "办公室沙发", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-14T07:30:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 61, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110600y0krwQZFp5AVcjqX.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t办公室的沙发通常要满足工作和休息等多样的需求，这组沙发是专为办公室设计的，来自西班牙工作室 OOO My Design。它有两种形式，一种是单人沙发带一张边桌，可以在桌子旁边放一张凳子。另一种是双人沙发，其中一边是脚踏，可以将两张沙发拼在一起。两种沙发都半开放的，只有单边扶手，因而也没有固定的朝向，方便使用者灵活转动。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150527fjgxpPzmaRSoILFW.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"772\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7352381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150528cQN8TYUvdyIVAhGx.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"742\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150528cIX6RdslrFeOP1uW.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"742\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150529ZOz3Dhsb87IKdoqQ.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"742\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150530SYEoiBNlXk5zcRtg.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"742\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}